    "title": "v---your-fear-of-the-monster-is-really-a-kind-of-desire...",
    "date": "25-07-26",
    "description": "By including a self portrait as the final image, I want to get across how trans people can fall into seeing ourselves through the mocking and hostile gaze of cis society. I also want it to work as an anticlimax to show the absurdity of their reactions - after all that, this is what you were looking at?",
    "contenttype": "Photography"
  },
